N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 79.32 - Payment of prescribed parking fees required

State Regulations

No person shall park a vehicle within any public vehicular
parking area of the airport except upon the payment of such fees and charges as
may from time to time be prescribed. Notes
